#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Online Help"
msgstr "Spletna pomoč"

#. Tag: date
#: index.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "2018-04-01"
msgstr "1. 4. 2018"

#. Tag: releaseinfo
#: index.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applications 18.04"
msgstr "Applications 18.04"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this page, you can find different ways to find online help and additional "
"information provided by the &kde; community."
msgstr ""
"Na tej strani najdete različne načine za iskanje spletne pomoči in dodatnih "
"informacij, ki jih zagotavlja skupnost &kde;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; UserBase"
msgstr "&kde; Baza uporabnikov"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/"
"An_introduction_to_KDE\">An Introduction to &kde;</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/"
"An_introduction_to_KDE\">Uvod v &kde;</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Learn more about the <ulink url=\"https://kde.org/community/whatiskde/\"> "
"&kde; community and its software</ulink> and find information to help you "
"get started. Also, discover what <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/"
"Special:myLanguage/Welcome_to_KDE_UserBase\"> UserBase</ulink> is and how it "
"can help you."
msgstr ""
"Izvedite več o <ulink url=\"https://kde.org/community/whatiskde/\"> &kde; "
"skupnosti in njeni programski opremi</ulink> ter poiščite informacije, ki "
"vam bodo pomagale začeti. Spoznajte tudi, kaj je <ulink url=\"https://"
"userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Welcome_to_KDE_UserBase\"> UserBase</"
"ulink> in kako vam lahko pomaga."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Getting_Help"
"\">Getting Help</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Getting_Help"
"\">Pridobivanje pomoči</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Need some help? Here are some suggested places where you can get help with "
"problems, as well some hints on how to improve the quality of answers you "
"receive."
msgstr ""
"Potrebujete pomoč? Tukaj je nekaj predlogov, kje lahko dobite pomoč pri "
"težavah, in nekaj nasvetov, kako izboljšati kakovost prejetih odgovorov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Applications"
"\">Applications</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Applications"
"\">Aplikacije</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Discover the wide variety of applications from the &kde; Community, and find "
"out what program suits your needs and preferences."
msgstr ""
"Odkrijte široko paleto aplikacij iz skupnosti &kde; in ugotovite, kateri "
"program ustreza vašim potrebam in željam."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Tutorials"
"\">Tutorials</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Tutorials"
"\">Vadnice</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"How-To's, Tips &amp; Tricks that can help make your &kde; software "
"experience more enjoyable and productive."
msgstr ""
"Kako ravnati, nasveti in triki, ki vam lahko pomagajo, da bo vaša izkušnja s "
"programsko opremo &kde; prijetnejša in produktivnejša."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; Forum"
msgstr "&kde; Forum"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://forum.kde.org/\">&kde; Community Forums</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://forum.kde.org/\">Forumi &kde; skupnosti</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kde; Forums offer users, developers and people interested in &kde; a "
"place to help each other, discuss &kde;-related topics and exchange ideas. "
"You can find <ulink url=\"https://forum.kde.org/viewforum.php?f=14/"
"\">Tutorials &amp; Tips</ulink> in the forum."
msgstr ""
"Forumi &kde; nudijo uporabnikom, razvijalcem in ljudem, ki jih zanima &kde;, "
"prostor za medsebojno pomoč, razpravo o temah, povezanih z &kde;, in "
"izmenjavo idej. Na forumu lahko najdete <ulink url=\"https://forum.kde.org/"
"viewforum.php?f=14/\">Vadnice &amp; Nasvete</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; Techbase"
msgstr "&kde; Techbase"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "<ulink url=\"https://techbase.kde.org/\">&kde; Techbase</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr "<ulink url=\"https://techbase.kde.org/\">&kde; Techbase</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Information for developers and help to set up a &kde; development "
"environment."
msgstr "Informacije za razvijalce in pomoč pri vzpostavitvi razvojnega okolja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; Documentation"
msgstr "&kde; Dokumentacija"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://docs.kde.org/\">&kde; Documentation site</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://docs.kde.org/\">&kde; Stran z dokumentacijo</"
"ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This page holds the complete &kde; User Documentation in over 25 languages "
"for the released and the development version of &kde-frameworks;, &plasma-"
"workspaces; and &applications;."
msgstr ""
"Na tej strani je na voljo celotna uporabniška dokumentacija &kde; v več kot "
"25 jezikih za izdane in razvojne različice &kde-frameworks;, &plasma-"
"workspaces; in &applications;."
